(firstQuint)Phase III Study of 5LGr to Treat Tic Disorder.

 5LGr is a kind of traditional Chinese medicine(TCM) which under the direction of TCM theory.

The aim of this study is prove the effective and safety of 5LGr in children and adolescence of Tic syndrome sub-population with specific TCM syndrome differentiation, when compared with tiapride and placebo.

